  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mech Survivor Elite</strong> is a time-based survival game with action-packed gameplay and roguelite elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Buddy, an Elite Mech Operator for the Company. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a rogue AI corrupts the Company's robots, turning them against humanity, Buddy becomes the last hope. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face relentless waves of enemies and find out: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054480/extras/94dfe296f6adef4fc5a472f79306dc54.poster.avif?t=1767084679\" width=326 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054480/extras/94dfe296f6adef4fc5a472f79306dc54.webm?t=1767084679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054480/extras/94dfe296f6adef4fc5a472f79306dc54.mp4?t=1767084679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mech Survivor Elite</strong> is a time-based survival game with action-packed gameplay and roguelite elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Buddy, an Elite Mech Operator for the Company. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a rogue AI corrupts the Company's robots, turning them against humanity, Buddy becomes the last hope. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face relentless waves of enemies and find out: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054480/extras/94dfe296f6adef4fc5a472f79306dc54.poster.avif?t=1767084679\" width=326 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054480/extras/94dfe296f6adef4fc5a472f79306dc54.webm?t=1767084679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054480/extras/94dfe296f6adef4fc5a472f79306dc54.mp4?t=1767084679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
